{"tid":435564,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想幫有經濟困難既同學補數","createTime":"2017-10-14T11:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T17:15:20.000Z","uid":8286,"like":144,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"69679d29c3c98829912c07921992774f2c300f6b","tid":435564,"uid":8286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"小弟今年剛剛畢業，一直都好想幫一啲有需要既同學仔義補，而呢段時間比較空閒，所以想做返一啲有意義既事同彌補下四年有諗過但冇做過呢件事既遺憾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自已既少少背景：<br />\n- 四年都一直有補開習，主要都係補開maths，雖然dse我都只係得5，m1都係得5，但都有信心可以幫到一啲數學比較差既同學(可能係想拎4/5既同學)，所以都係主要教呢類型既同學，自己都喜歡用易明既例子解釋一啲concept 多於不停操數。<br />\n- 可能自己都係窮拎出身，所以都真係好想幫到啲有需要既同學，希望佢地可以升到大學，讀自己有興趣、想讀既科。<br />\n- 可能係大學文化同自己take既科既影響，我自己覺得教育除左教工具性既知識，都想同學可以了解自己想做啲咩，可以搵到意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點補法：<br />\n- 會好輕鬆咁補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 最主要我都係會做書入面既題目，因為其實嗰堆數都夠做，同如果理解到啲concept就可以識做好多，會做啲難啲既題目，如果係中六既同學就會做會考同dse卷。有咩問題都可以隨時問我。<br />\n- 如果其他科有咩問題都歡迎搵我解答，例如中史通識econ<br />\n<br />\n時間、地方：<br />\n- 因為暫時未有工作在身（裸辭咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），所以可以大家傾下點樣方便啲<br />\n- 最好都係喺大埔、粉嶺、沙田都得，可能會喺M記，可能喺中大<br />\n<br />\n揀人準則：<br />\n- 首先要真係有需要，尤其係未必有能力出去私補/補習社但又想數學有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (真係真係有需要)<br />\n- 其次係有心，會理解下啲concept，會返去自己做下練習。<br />\n- 因為第一次義補，所以暫時只係想幫一個同學先，一星期可能補一兩日。當下主要想幫中四至中六既同學，Retake既同學都得，希望可以跟到你考DSE。<br />\n<br />\n我知道自己既力量可能好薄弱，但都想盡一分力去幫助其他有需要既人，如果你/你知道有人好想補習但又未必有能力補，有興趣了解多啲的話就喺telegram搵<a href=\"https://t.me/hahahehehohoho。sorry，唔係好識用telegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhahahehehohoho%E3%80%82sorry%EF%BC%8C%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E8%AD%98%E7%94%A8telegram&d=qhykyEhMnRht1cruuPfc5TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6362b8ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hahahehehohoho。sorry，唔係好識用telegram</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465f6e6be4421c3343abfc5b4ae32f97e4ce0cac","tid":435564,"uid":24582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5337cf50d5e399293ceeebd7f771284a7052f4","tid":435564,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"車馬費都唔收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1e5164d1c2508dc1728736a265f92a825aa7c6","tid":435564,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（希望唔好幾年後就變成補習cap水天王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fe3b0798e0b48d2841f42ad4fd79e59a6a4fca","tid":435564,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"好有心 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dad3c220297fa074afe88ce64c48dcf9aab2ae7","tid":435564,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"難得咁有心"},{"pid":"120edb322b1b5985b89dddbc72f87a480acb71a3","tid":435564,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d85089ad6e481bb6a990235af871af29808ed3cd","tid":435564,"uid":89249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"幫推 如果有需要既我都可以幫手答dse數學問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3ae79bd0e44384f3a820fd4dcfe229f34b9562","tid":435564,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"鏡中月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmo