b3","tid":435564,"uid":8286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"首先好多謝你地對小弟既鼓勵，但我知道好多巴絲打都好有心去幫有需要既人，而我自己都係膽操操咁試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於大學既數暫時都恕我無能為力住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都想幫啲dse既同學仔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到有啲巴打話都想幫手教，而有啲同學仔可能住得比較遠，所以我之後可能會開個tg grp，同學仔有問題的話就可以dum上去個grp到問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時想限定個grp係20人到，所以如果有興趣教既巴絲打(如果有m1/m2底的話就更好了)同有興趣入呢個grp既同學仔都可以tg我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ccf5f96c988131563705999a153330745620ff","tid":435564,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"樓主好心地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5cb9f9bc8b74879c1e293b15a301cf53cfb112","tid":435564,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"889f6e41bcac5a5a3853cb5c3699154a757b4a09","tid":435564,"uid":134801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bcd50c52fb3479aa1760c3499b098d787786a1","tid":435564,"uid":108215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"支持👍🏻👍🏻"},{"pid":"dcd351d21be44822cba29cc3c074778cdd3432b9","tid":435564,"uid":86446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先好多謝你地對小弟既鼓勵，但我知道好多巴絲打都好有心去幫有需要既人，而我自己都係膽操操咁試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於大學既數暫時都恕我無能為力住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都想幫啲dse既同學仔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到有啲巴打話都想幫手教，而有啲同學仔可能住得比較遠，所以我之後可能會開個tg grp，同學仔有問題的話就可以dum上去個grp到問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時想限定個grp係20人到，所以如果有興趣教既巴絲打(如果有m1/m2底的話就更好了)同有興趣入呢個grp既同學仔都可以tg我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴線 , 原來香港真係有好人<br />\n但補一個太少, 同埋可能會俾人話想溝仔 / 女, 建議盡可能同時補 2,3 個"},{"pid":"e09033d7d7f5f97c6602596068d07d02f8882026","tid":435564,"uid":135827,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:29:33.000Z","msg":"可唔可以搭單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講返自己少少背景先，2017DSE數學5**(M2 5)，讀緊HKU哂銀時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有港島(最好南區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )嘅中四至中六甚或retake嘅同學想搵人幫下手教下你Core Math都可以搵我。M2就我唔太敢教，因為得5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以tg我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/adgjmptw23456789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fadgjmptw23456789&d=qhykyEhMnRht1cruuPfc5TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b4ef7746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/adgjmptw23456789</a>"},{"pid":"adb3b23dfc85dc47ad2c289484084ac9de6cb5e6","tid":435564,"uid":135827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:30:39.000Z","msg":"btw支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2853b97907a6c767d6e75fc61895c4c3e9ac46e5","tid":435564,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:33:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"826cc58439c869f4d38f150d89fc72267777bc5a","tid":435564,"uid":138728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:35:39.000Z","msg":"我遲兩届考就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:MATH Lv 4"},{"pid":"9ab5717defe5852f447aad5e533919ad8b4ce04b","tid":435564,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"fab17019d6a7ef4cec4ef403281c028d355766f8","tid":435564,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bea891eca35f8b0ba3c7077012181f5ea11cc82","tid":435564,"uid":152588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T21:16:30.000Z","msg":"免費？"},{"pid":"2b295d8d442725e8cc5a850fcc76b6261f0ff509","tid":435564,"uid":8286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>免費？</blockquote><br />\n係，但前題係真係有需要、有經濟困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fb1f3f2274371d353e303b5e9cc494117be55b","tid":435564,"uid":20848,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"好難得，同樓主一樣，都想幫下DSE嘅學生。<br />\n<br />\n但我就想影響力大D, 因為覺得咁樣一個人幫到嘅人數唔係好多，所以我以家都出緊D DSE Newsletter比學生，入面又有resources, 又有唔同科嘅大學生分享佢地DSE心得咁，暫時都有1500個學生subscribe左，希望可以從另一個方向幫到佢地。<br />\n<br />\n樓主或其他有相同理念嘅巴絲打有興趣睇下點樣可以一齊幫手或者想知多D嘅tg我傾下，多一個人多一分力量<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/AfterSchool_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAfterSchool_HK&d=qhykyEhMnRht1cruuPfc5TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=aba3f5f5\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/AfterSchool_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：見到學生WhatsApp多謝我嘅時候覺得好有滿足感，知道自己做緊學生真係需要嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602283a1ba01199ca94bcd5247e3a53d56fe6737","tid":435564,"uid":84854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7388de650d77eae250eda5d75581177d52b0442","tid":435564,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"雖然非常欣賞樓主，但係得lv5夠唔夠做架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0023078977b7e599de87a86960413976a